{"tid":640751,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙基利入一入黎","createTime":"2018-04-24T13:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T05:05:04.000Z","uid":17842,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e50d368c5a118e74093b7a4edfcefad5578bf84b","tid":640751,"uid":17842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T13:33:44.000Z","msg":"三巨頭都沒死<br />\n<br />\n洛基第一個死<br />\n<br />\n幻視在寶石分離後死去 寶石是被女巫分離而不是敵人<br />\n<br />\n其余英雄被滅霸全滅（瓦坎達）<br />\n<br />\n美隊1的反派紅骷髏會登場 告訴滅霸靈魂寶石如何獲得<br />\n<br />\n靈魂寶石 是 卡魔拉 卡魔拉被滅霸親手獻祭後取得靈魂寶石<br />\n<br />\n奇異博士本來可以留下時間寶石 但是為了救托尼給了滅霸<br />\n<br />\n蜘蛛俠就差一點就把滅霸的手套拿下來 還是失敗了<br />\n<br />\n雷神的新武器很牛逼 貫穿了滅霸但滅霸死不了<br />\n<br />\n滅霸最後集齊了所有寶石<br />\n<br />\n彩蛋尼克局長登場 召喚驚奇隊長<br />\n<br />\n星雲死的最慘 被分屍<br />\n<br />\n蟻人沒有登場<br />\n<br />\n影片整體基調悲傷 個別段落搞笑 如托尼和博士初次見面互相吐槽 還有浣熊雷神嘴炮<br />\n<br />\n還有...第二版預告結尾美隊單挑滅霸..那一拳是接下來了 之後被滅霸虐了一番 但是沒死 別擔心"},{"pid":"7224554441f215dd3547cb33c0a19539893d6a9e","tid":640751,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T13:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37fc7e3984d5c5b0caa06c5ffbd75881a347900c","tid":640751,"uid":41158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T13:34:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec565c0b70e2677341f5df2e159e0fd6e3a250e","tid":640751,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T13:34:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b70d16ec2d4455680e49a9d81b8f8ed3233f30f9","tid":640751,"uid":6070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T13:35:16.000Z","msg":